-> /etc/fstab
    ( settings file sistems for pluggable devices )
-> /etc/mtab
    ( mounted devices )
-> /etc/ld.so.conf
    ( path to system libs )
-> /etc/hosts
    ( network settings )
-> /etc/resolve.conf
    ( DNS settings )
-> /etc/host.conf or /etc/nsswitch.conf
    ( set determination procedure ip by domain names )
-> /etc/syslog.conf
    ( settings for logging journal )